# Li Shuk Fan v Director of Immigration——FACV 2，3/2001
# Ng Siu Tung v Director of Immigration——FACV 1/2001
# Next Magazine Publishing Ltd. v Man Ching Fat——FACV 5/2002
# HKSAR v Wong Sau Ming——FACC 5/2002
# Leung Kwok Hung; Fung Ka Keung Christopher; Lo Wai Ming v HKSAR——FACC 1,2/2005
